# Committed empty placeholders for go:embed so the launcher compiles and
# `go test ./...` runs on a clean checkout (e.g. Linux/macOS dev machines).
# Windows build scripts (build/embed-payload.ps1, build/fetch-cryptopro-plugin.ps1)
# overwrite these with the real payload/plugin archives during a build.
# No CryptoPro binaries are committed: both files are zero-byte placeholders.
!internal/bootstrap/payload.zip
!internal/bootstrap/cryptopro-plugin.zip
